com.cleo.lexicom.external

Class RegistrationInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cleo.lexicom.external.RegistrationInfo

  • public class RegistrationInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    RegistrationInfo is used to receive and potentially modify registration information during licensing. Refer to ILicenser.registrationQuery(String) and ILicenser.register(RegistrationInfo).
